response.overview: Taking inspiration from Peter M. Bracke's definitive book of the same name, this seven-hour documentary dives into the making of all twelve Friday the 13th films, with all-new interviews from the cast and the crew.
response.tagline: The ultimate tribute to one of horror's most iconic and enduring franchises
